flowchart TD
  U[ADMIN / RECEPTIONIST / DOCTOR / PATIENT] --> C[Appointment Servlet]
  C --> S[AppointmentService]
  S --> O{Role and ownership allowed?}
  O -- No --> X[403 / safe failure + audit]
  O -- Yes --> A[AvailabilityService]
  A --> SD[ScheduleDao]
  A --> AD[AppointmentDao: booked starts]
  A --> DD[DoctorDao]
  SD --> G[TimeSlotGenerator]
  G --> E[Exclude booked and elapsed slots]
  E --> S
  S --> PD[PatientDao]
  S --> CF{Doctor or patient conflict?}
  CF -- Yes --> B[Block + audit]
  CF -- No --> TX[JDBC transaction]
  TX --> AD
  AD --> ORA[(Oracle XE)]
  S --> RS[Reschedule: exclude current appointment]
  S --> ST[Status transition state machine]
  RS --> TX
  ST --> TX
